397
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:05,451
Ali.

398
00:29:13,793 --> 00:29:15,711
Milagre.

399
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,671
Eu nem tinha certeza
que era verdade.

400
00:29:19,758 --> 00:29:21,383
